# Basic Firewall Configuration using UFW on Ubuntu (VirtualBox)

## Objective
To configure a basic firewall using UFW on Ubuntu running inside VirtualBox.

## Environment
- Ubuntu OS
- VirtualBox Virtual Machine

## Configuration Steps
- Installed UFW
- Denied all incoming connections by default
- Allowed outgoing connections
- Allowed SSH (port 22)
- Denied HTTP (port 80)
- Enabled firewall and verified rules

## Files
- ufw_configuration.sh
- Screenshot of ufw status

